                                                                                                                                                               TThe one thing bobertron liked to do is help the needy. He kept an open frequency to all happenings. He overheard a battle between a maxi cheetor and some odd quickstrike. HE noticed as quickstrike and the two females were carrying him off that they were on direct route to where he planned to meet tthe new maximal longhunter. HE would eventualy encounter them any way so he decided he better at least have the element of surprise. Bobertron tararize! He transformed into his robot mode and jumped down and gave a quick shot to quickestrikes head. Before they new what was happening bobertron grabbed the cat and flew off. Immedidatley he comm magmatron im gonna need some help here. Im gonna have three pissed off guys on my tail in a nano click so move your ass!                                                                 Talon Harvilicz <wilddance_mare@...> wrote: 
Quickstrike:



"Ah'm fine," he said, keeping his head down. It was just his foot. "Ah had 
worse. Really." He looked back at the two females. "Th' base ain't far. It's 
one klick from here." He grabbed a hold of Cheetor's legs. "One of y'all 
ladies get his front."
